summary: It's a perfectly generic item. Perhaps a bit too perfect.
descriptionHtml:
It's a perfectly generic item. Perhaps a bit too perfect.

This Item is originally from the webcomic Homestuck

Ever played Starbound?
Sometimes when i played this game i got a missing item or made a faulty mod recipe. Then this missing item appears as a Perfectly Generic Item ingame.

So i want to make the same faulty mod recipe for Skyrim. And share this wonderful Perfectly Generic Items with oder Skyrim Players.

Its craftable as a misc item at any forge.
You aks what you should do with it?
You can throw it at Skeevers, give it to Brenuin, or spam your E button to lift you Smithing Skill to the Stars.

Have fun Starbounders and Dovahkiins.

You can feel free to modify this mod and share it with others ;)
author: MazeRaze
